snippet.title: Mario Builder 64 | ROM Hack Release & Download
snippet.description:
Mario Builder 64 is a Super Mario 64 level editor created by Rovertronic and @Arthurtilly.

- Download -
RHDC: https://romhacking.com/hack/mario-builder-64
GB: https://gamebanana.com/mods/514361
GH: https://github.com/rovertronic/Mario-Builder-64

- Setup Guide -
Video: https://youtu.be/yMj60UtyQnE
Read: https://rentry.co/mb64-setup-guide

- Trailer Music -
Offenbach - Orpheus in the Underworld, Overture (w/Can-Can) (Super Mario 64 Soundfont)
Uploaded by: Classical Entertainment System
https://youtu.be/ALJJo8CJAxU

- Patreons -
Blob Jelly, Popeto, Qacher Gigdu, Disturbing Nose, TOFU, Haffey, Pizza Brian, ZT, Henry Kümpel

- Social Links -
▶️ 2nd Channel: https://www.youtube.com/@twovert
😊 Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/rovertronic
🗨 Discord: https://discord.gg/X7vvvKu
⭐ RHDC: https://romhacking.com/user/rovertronic

🐔
